@ajdroid 
The way I avoided the bug was to avoid the line `a[elt_idx] = out + a[elt_idx]`

In my case, the Tensor I had was sparsely populated so I could afford to just collect everything into different variables and only sum all of them at the end. That made the problem go away for me.
